That being said; STRAWBERRY DIESEL IS A WONDERFUL, HAPPY, EUPHORIC, CONTROL THE DEPRESSION, SPECIAL STRAIN.

“Strawberry Diesel is an incredible high, an awesome medicine, and definitely one of the best strains I've tried. It did cause SEVERE dry eyes, Ben Stein style, so make sure you have eye drops handy! Other than that, I had a great case of the giggles, made me very happy. I slept like a rock after, too. This strain is great.. Right up there with Chernobyl, Girlscout Cookie, and Dead Dawg.”

“I've been using this strain for over a month now for chronic pain, and my wife has used it with good results as well for gastrointestinal issues. I don't know who the breeder was of the strain that I received in clone form and grew myself, but it's definitely diesely" with a berry
column4: or fruity overtone. It's a bit harsh
column5: and will get coughin' if you're not careful

“I find myself paranoid/anxious on this - if I didn't have better mental discipline, I'd have a panic attack. In fact, I've been working exclusively on 1/8 I bought recently, and I'd say that this strain has been triggering neurosis in me consistently.

If I stay positive, it helps me figure things out. But if I get negative, and dwell on my fears, it also helps me figure those things out - in a bad way - by opening...”

“This strain is good for beginners, as it gives a balanced high and doesn't induce very much paranoia. On the other hand if you are an experienced smoker looking to get some good stuff, you might not be super impressed with the overall high, or at least I wasn't. But overall not that bad, but not super great.”

“Amazing fruity and pine fragrance/taste. Happiest high I've ever had, this stuff just makes you feel universally content. Smoked two bowls--the effects lasted around 1.5-2 hours and after they wore off I felt pretty tired. Overall this is great stuff, I'd imagine it'd be perfect just to smoke while hanging out with friends, makes you happy, giggly, and sociable.”
“one of my favorites so far! A good head high, with the relaxation of a body high. A good strawberry after taste, and also smells awesome!”
“My personal favorite great relaxing feel.”

“Great for indoor growing. Grows many branches (outward if topped) with heavy, super super dense buds that smell piney/earthy with strawberry notes definitely in there, especially when grown well. Because buds are sooo dense, mold/spider mites tend to love it also (go figure). 
Very strong initial high that doesn't last too long but can be used for pain relief fairly quick.  The high is certainly heavy" and can prod...”"

“This is a beautiful girl, my daughter named her strawberry shortcake. The sheriff just left my dog had to go to court today her name is cookie" she is a healer lab cross and she herded the neighbor. I was going to tell ya'll about it. But i smoked 5 hits from a bowl for this review that's an extra hit of medication for me and I feel like I just ate a xanax. This is a beautiful strain I could just melt into the couch...”"

“4.5 out of 5.  First look reveals medium popcorn like bugs with a slight airyness but very resiny, sugary, and denser at the core. Lime green leaves and buds with a few orange and purple hairs, real Beaut. Smell is immediate skunky with diesel and fruit undertones. Grinds to niiiice amount of stickiness and moisture, doesn't stick to your hands but rolls out to a nice Joint. PERFECT example of a nice hybrid, Pain rel...”

“I didn't find the effects of this strain as pronounced as other reviewers. There was undoubtedly a bout of drowsiness associated but not so powerful as to curb my insomnia. I am a daily smoker; in the past few weeks smoking this strain I have found it to induce creativity but stifle timeliness. Definite dry-mouth with a rather pungent aftertaste (as is to be expected with a Sour Diesel hybrid). Good taste and aroma. ...”

“*RAW DIESEL* 
Pretty mello high. Very Sativa like by really only giving a buzz from the shoulders up. A very fun smoke for day time. It's a good smoke, just one you'd have to keep up a system to smoke all day. Zero sleepiness and no munchies. However it is a very short lived smoke. The high last barely an hour it seemed. Pretty mello”

“The smell of this strain is similar to pink lemonade which makes this strain very intriguing. The high is not too strong with a nice cerebral high and light body high. When medicating to this strain I noticed slight paranoia but it only lasted about 2 minutes and after wards music and stand up comedy could not have sounded any better. I would recommend this strain for time that needs to be given to yourself.”

But, when i smoked more then normal it's good for it's nighttime Indica effects.”
